org.pepstock.charba.client.commons

Class ChartContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.JavaScriptObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.ChartContainer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Arc, Axis, BaseTick, CartesianScaleLabel, Elements, EventProvider, GridLines, Hover, Layout, LegendLabels, Line, Padding, Padding, Point, RadialAngleLines, RadialPointLabels, Rectangle, Scales, Time, Title, Tooltips

    public abstract class ChartContainer
extends JavaScriptObjectContainer
    Extends a JavaScript object container for all entities which needs the chart instance.
    This class is used for all entities which will trigger events or callbacks to pass the chart instance as parameter of implemented interface.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero

    JavaScriptObjectContainer
